Village of HambsharevillagenM0none765793690searchvar1.46335******02*The roofs of its houses are all the same colour: blue. The very conservative community is to blame for this, not that it makes the village ugly, but because it's almost impossible to get anything but old gossip from these villagers. It is unlikely that you will want to come back here again, except if you know someone you like here, which would be as unlikely.